a small red book by Mao.

204
00:08:35,842 --> 00:08:40,058
Their job was to target those who were against Mao.

205
00:08:40,058 --> 00:08:45,206
Intellectuals, party officials, all those
who were not loyal to Mao's ideology,

206
00:08:45,206 --> 00:08:48,625
were targeted, publicly humiliated

207
00:08:48,625 --> 00:08:51,530
