208
00:08:51,530 --> 00:08:54,179
There were people in the Communist Party who

209
00:08:54,179 --> 00:08:56,472
were criticizing the Cultural Revolution,

210
00:08:56,472 --> 00:08:57,749
criticizing Mao,

211
00:08:57,749 --> 00:09:00,695
and they were also targeted
by the Red Guards.

212
00:09:00,695 --> 00:09:03,415
Liu Shaoqi and Deng Xiaoping

213
00:09:03,415 --> 00:09:07,094
were some of the high-ranking party officials,

214
