244
00:10:35,147 --> 00:10:38,298
But it is not that there were only failures and bad things

245
00:10:38,298 --> 00:10:39,236
during Mao's reign.

246
00:10:39,236 --> 00:10:40,933
There were some positive achievements too.

247
00:10:40,933 --> 00:10:44,352
Especially in terms of women's equality and education.

248
00:10:44,352 --> 00:10:48,113
A nationwide public education system was launched during Mao's rule.

249
00:10:48,113 --> 00:10:51,648
Campaigns were run by the government to end illiteracy.

250
00:10:51,648 --> 00:10:53,284
And during Mao's leadership,

251
